                <p><i class="fa fa-check-square text-primary me-3"></i><strong>CAD design and modeling:</strong> Visualizing and refining systems through precision CAD tools.</p>
                <p><i class="fa fa-check-square text-primary me-3"></i><strong>Design review and approval:</strong> Client collaboration to ensure satisfaction and design approval.</p>
